														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2064492">
									

<p>I also don't like how you seemed to completely ignore this story when you explained the origin of the CI.<br />
<a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/slate-thunder">http://www.scp-wiki.net/slate-thunder</a><br />
This is a really great story and I feel that it wasn't necessary for you to give a new story about how the CI was created that wasn't nearly as good. There is nothing wrong with making up your own story about how the CI was started (after all there are many origin stories for the Foundation), but if you don't do a good enough job of it while completely ignoring a better story about it then it's bad.</p>

